  "text": "The peer-reviewed analysis of the ATAC trial appeared in the Lancet in June 2002 [CITATION_1] . Between March 2002 and July 2002, the use of anastrozole rose from 14%-22% of primary adjuvant hormonal therapies (p < 0.05).",
